<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#20a3182b920b6242366c11f02a18386a>.
<#20a3182b920b6242366c11f02a18386a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/70c69e3f-22b0-4d4f-9976-a4479428de24>;
