<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d64c3388-6be6-48e4-84ef-c0586016869f> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Öppna data"@sv, "Inspire"@sv, "Observation"@sv, "Oceanografi"@sv, "Alger"@sv, "Havsområden"@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/OTHER>;
