<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d554a139a43d531f741bc712a64eef73>.
<#d554a139a43d531f741bc712a64eef73> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bb9e6017459328e59935373f9a85d72a>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.098Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#d554a139a43d531f741bc712a64eef73> {
<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bb9e6017459328e59935373f9a85d72a> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "citizen science"@en, "medborgarforskning"@sv, "Artificiell intelligens"@sv, "Artificial Intelligence"@en, "Fästingar"@sv, "Ticks"@en, "image analysis"@en, "image classification"@en, "bildklassifiering"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__2536.
_:b0__2536 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/author>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021001868>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bb9e6017459328e59935373f9a85d72a> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021001868>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This dataset contains all verified reports of tick sightings with corresponding images reported by the public to the \"Rapportera Fästing\" platform (https://rapporterafasting.sva.se/) during 2025 The platform is developed and maintained by the Swedish Veterinary Agency (SVA) within the scope of the European project IDAlert (https://idalertproject.eu/). The dataset is provided by SVA and is licensed under CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/).\n\nThe dataset includes two files: ticks_2025.zip, which contains the tick image files, and ticks_2025.csv, which contains metadata about each report. Note that the verification is done on report level, and thus all images may not necessarily contain ticks, but at least one image per report has been verified as a tick by experts at SVA. The dataset contains 11,901 unique images from 9080 reports."@en, "Detta dataset innehåller alla verifierade rapporter om fästingobservationer med tillhörande bilder som allmänheten har rapporterat till plattformen ”Rapportera Fästing” (https://rapporterafasting.sva.se/) under 2025. Plattformen utvecklas och underhålls av Statens veterinärmedicinska anstalt (SVA) inom ramen för det europeiska projektet IDAlert (https://idalertproject.eu/). Datasetet tillhandahålls av SVA och är licensierat under CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/).\n\nDatasetet innehåller två filer: ticks_2025.zip, som innehåller bildfilerna på fästingar, och ticks_2025.csv, som innehåller metadata om varje rapport. Observera att verifieringen görs på rapportnivå, och att alla bilder därför inte nödvändigtvis innehåller fästingar, men att minst en bild per rapport har verifierats som en fästing av experter vid SVA. Datasetet innehåller 11 901 unika bilder från 9080 rapporter."@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/0ae9787aafa76e2936bbc4f361cd27aa>, <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/80aaed229b853d6e2e3461a85177a42a>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-03-25T08:13:21.95743Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-26T15:41:21.645532Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Images of Ticks Submitted to the Swedish Veterinary Agency During 2025"@en, "Fästingbilder som skickats in till Statens veterinärmedicinska anstalt under 2025"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__6947.
_:b0__6947 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2025-12-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2025-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bb9e6017459328e59935373f9a85d72a> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

