    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Kartlager som visar cykelpumpar i Malmö kommun.\n\n__Uppdateringsfrekvensen för denna datamängd är otillfredsställande. Malmö stad kommer att åtgärda detta inom kort.__  \n\nKoordinat system: ESPG 4326.    \nEngelska: Bike pumps.  \n\n## Data innehåller  \n__anlaggningsnummer__: Cykelpump nummer.  \n__Modell__: Typ.  \n__Årtal__: År.  \n\n\n"@sv, "Map layer showing bicycle pumps in Malmö municipality.\n\n**The update frequency for this data set is unsatisfactory. The City of Malmö\nwill fix this shortly.**\n\nCoordinate system: ESPG 4326.  \nEnglish: Bike pumps.\n\n##  Data contains\n\n**facility number** : Bicycle pump number.  \n**Model** : Type.  \n**Year** : Year.\n\n"@en, "Kortlag, der viser cykelpumper i Malmø Kommune.\n\n**Opdateringsfrekvensen for dette datasæt er utilfredsstillende. Malmø Kommune\nvil rette dette snarest.**\n\nKoordinatsystem: ESPG 4326.  \nEngelsk: Cykelpumper.\n\n##  Data indeholder\n\n**Facilitetsnummer** : Cykelpumpenummer.  \n**Model** : Type.  \n**År** : År.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__2499.
_:b0__2499 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/c6051c71-4d12-4c93-9966-1ad599430d03> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/abd7da407bcfbc956fd6c0e91189412f>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/c6051c71-4d12-4c93-9966-1ad599430d03/resource/071f8435-38e7-4f66-8ebf-9d10ddaa4f0f>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/c6051c71-4d12-4c93-9966-1ad599430d03/resource/c9a788fc-b47a-4de8-aeb8-f4f954d7bbd0>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/c6051c71-4d12-4c93-9966-1ad599430d03/resource/b60b3dbc-0c47-4ef9-b6f1-fac5b77acac6>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/c6051c71-4d12-4c93-9966-1ad599430d03/resource/aad5a414-52a4-4990-920a-d146ba6db959>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-09"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-18T20:26:09.893159"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
