<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#51748d8f73c0342077f5683d0072867d>.
<#51748d8f73c0342077f5683d0072867d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/9c865a15-3b77-4945-a5d6-e2b10da95643>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.129Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#51748d8f73c0342077f5683d0072867d> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/9c865a15-3b77-4945-a5d6-e2b10da95643> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "9c865a15-3b77-4945-a5d6-e2b10da95643";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "All data refers to students in schools with grades according to the goal- and\nknowledge-related grading system.\n\nStatistics in percentages from 2013.\n\nThe term \"location municipality\" refers to students in both municipal and\nindependent schools located in the municipality, regardless of where they are\nregistered.\n\nIf the total number of students is 40 or more and the number of EJ with the\nlowest grade E is 1-4 students, the percentage is shown as 95 percent.\n\nSource: Swedish National Agency for Education (Siris).\n\n"@en, "Alle data refererer til elever i skoler med karakterer i henhold til det mål-\nog vidensrelaterede karaktersystem.\n\nStatistik i procenter fra 2013.\n\nBegrebet \"lokationskommune\" henviser til elever i både kommunale og friskoler\nbeliggende i kommunen, uanset hvor de er indskrevet.\n\nHvis det samlede antal elever er 40 eller flere, og antallet af EJ med den\nlaveste karakter E er 1-4 elever, vises procentdelen som 95 procent.\n\nKilde: Den svenske statslige skolestyrelse (Siris).\n\n"@da, "Samtliga uppgifter avser elever i skolor med betyg enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet. \n\nStatistik i procent från 2013.\n\nMed lägeskommun avses elever i både kommunala och fristående skolor belägna i kommunen oavsett var de är folkbokförda. \n\nOm det totala antalet elever är 40 eller fler och antalet EJ med lägst betyget E är 1-4 elever, så visas andelen som 95 procent. \n\nKälla: Skolverket Siris)."@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__9978.
_:b0__9978 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/9c865a15-3b77-4945-a5d6-e2b10da95643> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/9c865a15-3b77-4945-a5d6-e2b10da95643/resource/f20c9a43-3231-4971-b50e-21c89045bbee>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-18T21:27:08.876489"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i årskurs 6 med lägsta betyget E  i engelska, lägeskommun"@sv, "Students in grade 6 with the lowest grade of E in English, location municipality"@en, "Elever i 6. klasse med den laveste karakter på E i engelsk, placeringskommune"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

