<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#a0be7d147ca38d8fde4b202baf064bc5>.
<#a0be7d147ca38d8fde4b202baf064bc5> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/39273cfc-aa1c-444a-8b72-6f27cd4a8db2>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.130Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#a0be7d147ca38d8fde4b202baf064bc5> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/39273cfc-aa1c-444a-8b72-6f27cd4a8db2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "39273cfc-aa1c-444a-8b72-6f27cd4a8db2";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Elevernas sammanlagda meritvärde dividerat med antal elever som fått betyg i minst ett ämne enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet i årskurs 9. \n\nStatistik från 2015.\n\n* Betygen mäts före prövning.  \n* Uppgifterna avser elever i kommunens egna skolor eller fristående skolor i kommunen, oavsett folkbokföringsort.  \n* Uppgiften avser läsår. \n*  2016 exkluderades elever med okänd bakgrund.  \n\nMeritvärdet för en elev utgörs av summan för de 17 bästa betygen i elevens slutbetyg  (E=10, D=12.5, C=15, B=17.5 och A=20). Det möjliga maxvärdet är 340 poäng. \n\nKälla: Skolverket (Siris)."@sv, "The students' total merit value divided by the number of students who received\na grade in at least one subject according to the goal- and knowledge-related\ngrading system in grade 9.\n\nStatistics from 2015.\n\n  * The grades are measured before the examination.\n  * The data refers to students in the municipality's own schools or independent schools in the municipality, regardless of place of population registration.\n  * The information refers to the academic year.\n  * In 2016, students with unknown backgrounds were excluded.\n\nThe credit value for a student is the sum of the 17 best grades in the\nstudent's final grade (E=10, D=12.5, C=15, B=17.5 and A=20). The maximum\npossible value is 340 points.\n\nSource: Swedish National Agency for Education (Siris).\n\n"@en, "Elevernes samlede meritværdi divideret med antallet af elever, der fik en\nkarakter i mindst ét ​​fag i henhold til det mål- og vidensrelaterede\nkaraktersystem i 9. klasse.\n\nStatistik fra 2015.\n\n  * Karaktererne måles før eksamen.\n  * Dataene vedrører elever i kommunens egne skoler eller friskoler i kommunen, uanset folkeregistreringssted.\n  * Oplysningerne refererer til studieåret.\n  * I 2016 blev studerende med ukendt baggrund udelukket.\n\nMeritværdien for en studerende er summen af ​​de 17 bedste karakterer i den\nstuderendes endelige karakter (E=10, D=12,5, C=15, B=17,5 og A=20). Den\nmaksimalt mulige værdi er 340 point.\n\nKilde: Den svenske statslige skolestyrelse (Siris).\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__9696.
_:b0__9696 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/39273cfc-aa1c-444a-8b72-6f27cd4a8db2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/39273cfc-aa1c-444a-8b72-6f27cd4a8db2/resource/266d4d8d-cef7-415c-bef1-ed3c8581c687>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-18T21:27:49.307634"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i årskurs 9 - genomsnitt av meritvärde, lägeskommun (17 ämnen)"@sv, "Students in grade 9 - average of merit value, location municipality (17 subjects)"@en, "Elever i 9. klasse - gennemsnit af meritværdi, placeringskommune (17 fag)"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4b9c78627d6b4842461559ee9940cf05>.
<#4b9c78627d6b4842461559ee9940cf05> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/1c44246c-e65d-431c-be4e-234c90ed1589>;
