<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f9721cbfede807b2366d357fe9476f96>.
<#f9721cbfede807b2366d357fe9476f96> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/a5dcbfe0-7610-4077-8b41-788b25d20114>;
