<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#86d24423235d56de76c4736ace9bbe9d>.
<#86d24423235d56de76c4736ace9bbe9d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/e0c53853-fe07-4175-9ba0-f496e474fec3>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.142Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#86d24423235d56de76c4736ace9bbe9d> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/e0c53853-fe07-4175-9ba0-f496e474fec3> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "e0c53853-fe07-4175-9ba0-f496e474fec3";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Antal elever i årskurs 9 som är behöriga till estetiska programmet dividerat med antal elever som fått eller skulle ha fått betyg i minst ett ämne enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet i årskurs 9. \n\nStatistik i procent från 2011.\n\nMed lägeskommun avses elever i skolor belägna i kommunen oavsett folkbokföringsort. \n\nUppgiften avser läsår. Om det totala antalet elever är 40 eller fler och antalet EJ behöriga är 1-4 elever, så visas andelen behöriga som 95 procent. 2016 exkluderades elever med okänd bakgrund. \n\nKälla: Skolverket (Siris)."@sv, "Number of students in grade 9 who are eligible for the aesthetics program\ndivided by the number of students who received or would have received a grade\nin at least one subject according to the goal- and knowledge-related grading\nsystem in grade 9.\n\nStatistics in percentages from 2011.\n\nThe term \"location municipality\" refers to students in schools located in the\nmunicipality, regardless of their place of population registration.\n\nThe information refers to the school year. If the total number of students is\n40 or more and the number of NOT eligible students is 1-4 students, the\npercentage of eligible students is shown as 95 percent. In 2016, students with\nunknown backgrounds were excluded.\n\nSource: Swedish National Agency for Education (Siris).\n\n"@en, "Antal elever i 9. klasse, der er berettigede til æstetikuddannelsen, divideret\nmed antallet af elever, der fik eller ville have fået en karakter i mindst ét\n​​fag i henhold til det mål- og vidensrelaterede karaktersystem i 9. klasse.\n\nStatistik i procenter fra 2011.\n\nBegrebet \"lokationskommune\" henviser til elever på skoler beliggende i\nkommunen, uanset deres folkeregistreringssted.\n\nOplysningerne refererer til skoleåret. Hvis det samlede antal elever er 40\neller mere, og antallet af IKKE-berettigede elever er 1-4 elever, vises\nprocentdelen af ​​berettigede elever som 95 procent. I 2016 blev elever med\nukendt baggrund udelukket.\n\nKilde: Den svenske statslige skolestyrelse (Siris).\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__5927.
_:b0__5927 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/e0c53853-fe07-4175-9ba0-f496e474fec3> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/e0c53853-fe07-4175-9ba0-f496e474fec3/resource/e6bd50f5-1fae-4dd7-b61d-8de4e98076d1>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T12:32:35.373678"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i årskurs 9 som är behöriga till estetiska programmet, lägeskommun"@sv, "Students in grade 9 who are eligible for the aesthetic program, location municipality"@en, "Elever i 9. klasse, der er berettigede til det æstetiske program, placeringskommune"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8116fc8f8e4ad67ec9a47acd3ad340b5>.
<#8116fc8f8e4ad67ec9a47acd3ad340b5> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/10e61518-3112-440c-9c1e-0ada2c5e2782>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.142Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#8116fc8f8e4ad67ec9a47acd3ad340b5> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/10e61518-3112-440c-9c1e-0ada2c5e2782> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "10e61518-3112-440c-9c1e-0ada2c5e2782";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Samtliga uppgifter avser elever i skolor med betyg enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet. \n\nStatistik i procent från 2013.\n\nMed lägeskommun avses elever i både kommunala och fristående skolor belägna i kommunen oavsett var de är folkbokförda. \n\nOm det totala antalet elever är 40 eller fler och antalet EJ med lägst betyget E är 1-4 elever, så visas andelen som 95 procent. \n\nKälla: Skolverket (Siris)."@sv, "All data refers to students in schools with grades according to the goal- and\nknowledge-related grading system.\n\nStatistics in percentages from 2013.\n\nThe term \"location municipality\" refers to students in both municipal and\nindependent schools located in the municipality, regardless of where they are\nregistered.\n\nIf the total number of students is 40 or more and the number of EJ with the\nlowest grade E is 1-4 students, the percentage is shown as 95 percent.\n\nSource: Swedish National Agency for Education (Siris).\n\n"@en, "Alle data refererer til elever i skoler med karakterer i henhold til det mål-\nog vidensrelaterede karaktersystem.\n\nStatistik i procenter fra 2013.\n\nBegrebet \"lokationskommune\" henviser til elever i både kommunale og friskoler\nbeliggende i kommunen, uanset hvor de er indskrevet.\n\nHvis det samlede antal elever er 40 eller flere, og antallet af EJ med den\nlaveste karakter E er 1-4 elever, vises procentdelen som 95 procent.\n\nKilde: Den svenske statslige skolestyrelse (Siris).\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__4764.
_:b0__4764 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/10e61518-3112-440c-9c1e-0ada2c5e2782> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/10e61518-3112-440c-9c1e-0ada2c5e2782/resource/96ddf207-492b-4f6f-9141-108ea1ad4bb1>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T12:33:49.619427"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i årskurs 6 med lägsta betyget E i matematik, lägeskommun"@sv, "Students in grade 6 with the lowest grade E in mathematics, location municipality"@en, "Elever i 6. klasse med den laveste karakter E i matematik, placeringskommune"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

