<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#172012746228f51e31e1ca3886717ef2>.
<#172012746228f51e31e1ca3886717ef2> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.145Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#172012746228f51e31e1ca3886717ef2> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "personbilar";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Visar antal personer boende i det valda området som har minst en personbil i trafik. Variabeln finns uppdelad på kön. Data från Transportstyrelsens bilregister.\n\n__Variabelbeskrivning__  \nHittar du [här](https://malmo.se/404)!  \n                     \n__API__  \nMed hjälp av API-anropet *https://opendata-api.malmo.se/api/3/action/resource_search?query=description:malm%C3%B6%20statistik* får man i JSON-format fram samtliga datamängder som innehåller statistikunderlag för Malmös områden.  \nI varje instans av result/results i JSON-resultatet finns för varje resurs en egenskap \"id\". Värdet för \"id\" kan användas för att hämta datan för respektive statistikvariabel (enligt värdet för egenskapen \"name\").\nAPI-anrop för att hämta statistikdatan: *https://opendata-api.malmo.se/api/action/datastore_search?resource_id=[id-värdet]*   \n\nAnvänd gärna siffrorna, men ange “Stadskontoret, Malmö stad” som källa."@sv, "Shows the number of people living in the selected area who have at least one\npassenger car in traffic. The variable is broken down by gender. Data from the\nSwedish Transport Agency's car register.\n\n**Variable description**  \nYou find it [here](https://malmo.se/404) !\n\n**APIs**  \nUsing the API call\n_https://opendata%2dapi.malmo.se/api/3/action/resource_search?query=description:malm%C3%B6%20statistics,_\nyou can retrieve all data sets that contain statistical data for Malmö's areas\nin JSON format.  \nIn each instance of result/results in the JSON result, there is an \"id\"\nproperty for each resource. The value of \"id\" can be used to retrieve the data\nfor the respective statistics variable (according to the value of the \"name\"\nproperty). API call to retrieve the statistics data:\n_https://opendata%2dapi.malmo.se/api/action/datastore_search?resource_id=[id\nvalue]_\n\nFeel free to use the numbers, but cite “City Office, Malmö City” as the\nsource.\n\n"@en, "Viser antallet af personer, der bor i det valgte område, og som har mindst én\npersonbil i trafikken. Variablen er opdelt efter køn. Data fra\nTrafikstyrelsens bilregister.\n\n**Variabelbeskrivelse**  \nDu finder det [her](https://malmo.se/404) !\n\n**API'er**  \nVed at bruge API-kaldet\n_https://opendata%2dapi.malmo.se/api/3/action/resource_search?query=description:malm%C3%B6%20statistics_\nkan du hente alle datasæt, der indeholder statistiske data for Malmøs områder,\ni JSON-format.  \nI hver forekomst af result/results i JSON-resultatet er der en \"id\"-egenskab\nfor hver ressource. Værdien af ​​\"id\" kan bruges til at hente dataene for den\nrespektive statistikvariabel (i henhold til værdien af ​​egenskaben \"name\").\nAPI-kald for at hente statistikdataene:\n_https://opendata%2dapi.malmo.se/api/action/datastore_search?resource_id=[id-\nværdi]_\n\nBrug gerne tallene, men angiv \"Bykontoret, Malmö Kommune\" som kilde.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__6426.
_:b0__6426 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/ce429264a6a97cd4bc8687f7a5b0847d>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb/resource/3d53a09f-d248-4a02-b366-24d670d9dc7a>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb/resource/cd35c422-8cc9-4619-aa98-e582a7c1da26>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-17"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T14:48:26.832941"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Bilägare - Statistikunderlag för Malmös områden"@sv, "Car owners - Statistical data for Malmö's areas"@en, "Bilejere - Statistiske data for Malmøs områder"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__3470.
_:b0__3470 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2007-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/bcfbcc67-22a8-440c-9778-35de3530e4fb> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#45abfd492ca6884dfe589e8f699bd73a>.
<#45abfd492ca6884dfe589e8f699bd73a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
