<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/73a8b10d-3f7c-49c5-b917-2dff38eaddf1> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/ce429264a6a97cd4bc8687f7a5b0847d>;
