<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#46e30ce8ed5af3da940da65c5f98a2ba>.
<#46e30ce8ed5af3da940da65c5f98a2ba> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/b5d3b02d-4133-4e7c-b58b-c1506a5882cf>;
