_:b0__3231 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/9ad34795-f16c-4f00-a7f1-ff964dab64cb> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/ce429264a6a97cd4bc8687f7a5b0847d>;
