    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/e5a1983c-eb1d-4132-b59e-fa6b4e00c826> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
