    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/aedc7084-1fd4-4923-bbdd-c71d1ef2ea7c>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.161Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#88128a1055edd7d1e28dd5b89cec17e2> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/aedc7084-1fd4-4923-bbdd-c71d1ef2ea7c> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "aedc7084-1fd4-4923-bbdd-c71d1ef2ea7c";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Andel elever med godkänt betyg i alla ämnen som ingått i elevens utbildning. \n\nAndelen beräknas på dem elever som fått eller skulle ha fått betyg enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet (elever som saknar godkänt betyg i alla ämnen ingår). \n\nStatistik i procent från 1998.\n\nUppgiften avser elever folkbokförda i kommunen oavsett var de går i skola. \n\nKälla: SCB och Skolverket."@sv, "Percentage of students with passing grades in all subjects included in the\nstudent's education.\n\nThe proportion is calculated on students who received or would have received\ngrades according to the goal- and knowledge-related grading system (students\nwho do not have a passing grade in all subjects are included).\n\nStatistics in percentages from 1998.\n\nThe data refers to students registered in the municipality regardless of where\nthey attend school.\n\nSource: Statistics Sweden and the Swedish National Agency for Education.\n\n"@en, "Procentdel af elever med beståede karakterer i alle fag, der indgår i elevens\nuddannelse.\n\nAndelen beregnes ud fra elever, der har modtaget eller ville have modtaget\nkarakterer i henhold til det mål- og vidensrelaterede karaktersystem (elever,\nder ikke har bestået i alle fag, er inkluderet).\n\nStatistik i procenter fra 1998.\n\nDataene omfatter elever, der er registreret i kommunen, uanset hvor de går i\nskole.\n\nKilde: Statistiska centralbanken og Skolstyrelsen.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__3228.
_:b0__3228 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/aedc7084-1fd4-4923-bbdd-c71d1ef2ea7c> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/aedc7084-1fd4-4923-bbdd-c71d1ef2ea7c/resource/c2e098a0-6683-422b-b50b-2d903ef94fa9>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T15:57:18.707785"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i årskurs 9 som uppnått kunskapskraven i alla ämnen, hemkommun"@sv, "Students in grade 9 who have achieved the knowledge requirements in all subjects, home municipality"@en, "Elever i 9. klasse, der har opnået videnskravene i alle fag, hjemkommune"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ffaa0305d24b203cd47acca72b596071>.
<#ffaa0305d24b203cd47acca72b596071> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/8909f747-c1f6-4205-9c61-9862545b52ea>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.162Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#ffaa0305d24b203cd47acca72b596071> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/8909f747-c1f6-4205-9c61-9862545b52ea> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "8909f747-c1f6-4205-9c61-9862545b52ea";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Samtliga uppgifter avser elever i skolor med betyg enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet. \n\nAntal elever i årskurs 6 med lägst betyg E i svenska inklusive svenska som andraspråk dividerat med antal elever som läst ämnet i årskurs 6. Multipliceras med 100 för redovisning i procent. \n\nStatistik i procent från 2013.\n\nAvser elever folkbokförda i kommunen oavsett var de går i skola. Elever med okänd bakgrund ingår. För dessa elever anges kommunen där de går i skolan som hemkommun. \n\nKälla: Skolverket och SCB."@sv, "All data refers to students in schools with grades according to the goal- and\nknowledge-related grading system.\n\nNumber of students in grade 6 with a minimum grade of E in Swedish including\nSwedish as a second language divided by the number of students who studied the\nsubject in grade 6. Multiply by 100 for reporting as a percentage.\n\nStatistics in percentages from 2013.\n\nRefers to students registered in the municipality regardless of where they\nattend school. Students with unknown backgrounds are included. For these\nstudents, the municipality where they attend school is stated as their home\nmunicipality.\n\nSource: Swedish National Agency for Education and Statistics Sweden.\n\n"@en, "Alle data refererer til elever i skoler med karakterer i henhold til det mål-\nog vidensrelaterede karaktersystem.\n\nAntal elever i 6. klasse med minimumskarakteren E i svensk, inklusive svensk\nsom andetsprog, divideret med antallet af elever, der studerede faget i 6.\nklasse. Gang med 100 for at rapportere som en procentdel.\n\nStatistik i procenter fra 2013.\n\nHenviser til elever, der er registreret i kommunen, uanset hvor de går i\nskole. Elever med ukendt baggrund er inkluderet. For disse elever er den\nkommune, hvor de går i skole, angivet som deres hjemkommune.\n\nKilde: Skolstyrelsen og Statistisk Centralbyrån.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__1443.
_:b0__1443 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/8909f747-c1f6-4205-9c61-9862545b52ea> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/8909f747-c1f6-4205-9c61-9862545b52ea/resource/de5d8832-1b69-44b2-a8a4-070aeefc5ca8>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T15:57:35.081013"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i årskurs 6 med lägsta betyget E i svenska, inklusive svenska som andraspråk, hemkommun"@sv, "Students in grade 6 with a minimum grade of E in Swedish, including Swedish as a second language, home municipality"@en, "Elever i 6. klasse med mindst karakteren E i svensk, inklusive svensk som andetsprog, hjemkommune"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#577fc194ec6e5b43fb517bd0fddea20b>.
<#577fc194ec6e5b43fb517bd0fddea20b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/6540f8e6-39d6-4ab9-82e3-199179c8ff3e>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.162Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#577fc194ec6e5b43fb517bd0fddea20b> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/6540f8e6-39d6-4ab9-82e3-199179c8ff3e> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "6540f8e6-39d6-4ab9-82e3-199179c8ff3e";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Antal folkbokförda elever i kommunen (hemkommunen) som började på gymnasium för 4 år sedan som fått examen eller studiebevis inom 4 år, (inklusive introduktionsprogram IM), dividerat med antal folkbokförda elever i kommunen som började på gymnasium för 4 år sedan, (inklusive IM). \n\nStatistik i procent från 2015.\n\nElever som vid utbildningens början saknar svenskt personnummer (exempelvis nyanlända elever som ännu inte blivit folkbokförda) ingår ej. \n\nEndast elever med  studiebevis om 2 500 poäng redovisas. \n\nKälla: SCB."@sv, "Number of registered students in the municipality (home municipality) who\nstarted upper secondary school 4 years ago who received a degree or study\ncertificate within 4 years, (including introductory program IM), divided by\nthe number of registered students in the municipality who started upper\nsecondary school 4 years ago, (including IM).\n\nStatistics in percentages from 2015.\n\nStudents who do not have a Swedish personal identification number at the\nbeginning of their education (for example, newly arrived students who have not\nyet been registered) are not included.\n\nOnly students with a study certificate of 2,500 points are reported.\n\nSource: Statistics Sweden.\n\n"@en, "Antal registrerede elever i kommunen (hjemkommunen), der startede i gymnasiet\nfor 4 år siden, og som modtog en uddannelse eller et studiebevis inden for 4\når (inklusive introduktionsprogram IM), divideret med antallet af registrerede\nelever i kommunen, der startede i gymnasiet for 4 år siden (inklusive IM).\n\nStatistik i procenter fra 2015.\n\nStuderende, der ikke har et svensk personnummer ved starten af ​​deres\nuddannelse (for eksempel nyankomne studerende, der endnu ikke er blevet\nregistreret), er ikke medregnet.\n\nKun studerende med et studiebevis på 2.500 point indberettes.\n\nKilde: Statistiska Centralbyrån.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__9473.
_:b0__9473 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/6540f8e6-39d6-4ab9-82e3-199179c8ff3e> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/6540f8e6-39d6-4ab9-82e3-199179c8ff3e/resource/04db943b-bc41-4eef-b3f0-19b6cbcb7b93>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T15:58:27.683971"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Gymnasieelever med examen eller studiebevis inom 4 år, hemkommun"@sv, "Upper secondary school students with a degree or certificate within 4 years, home municipality"@en, "Gymnasieelever med en uddannelse eller et certifikat inden for de sidste 4 år, hjemkommune"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4a24f7aecd6848a3f4b969550897b0a7>.
<#4a24f7aecd6848a3f4b969550897b0a7> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/4bc0a377-29f3-4bf6-94f2-a1ff243413a2>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:14.162Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#4a24f7aecd6848a3f4b969550897b0a7> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/4bc0a377-29f3-4bf6-94f2-a1ff243413a2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Malmö stad", "kolada", "statistik";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/ANNUAL>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "4bc0a377-29f3-4bf6-94f2-a1ff243413a2";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://malmo.se/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Antal elever år T-1 som var folkbokförda i kommunen, som avslutat gymnasium, , och som år T var etablerade på arbetsmarknaden eller studerade (inklusive Introduktionsprogrammet IM). Detta antal har dividerats med antal elever år T-1 som var folkbokförda i kommunen, som avslutat gymnasium, (inklusive IM). \n\n__Etablerad på arbetsmarknaden är den__  \n* som är sysselsatt enligt sysselsättningsregistrets definition (november månad)  \n* inte har några händelser som indikerar arbetslöshet eller  arbetsmarknadspolitiska åtgärder som inte är att betrakta som sysselsättning   \n* samt har haft en arbetsinkomst som inte understiger en gräns som är olika för varje år beroende på den genomsnittliga procentuella löneutvecklingen.  \n\nÅr 2016 var gränsen för att räknas som etablerad på arbetsmarknaden 191 800 kr. \n\nStuderande avser både högskolestudier och annan studiemedelsberättigad utbildning som exempelvis Komvux eller folkhögskola. \n\nKälla: SCB."@sv, "Number of students in year T-1 who were registered in the municipality, who\nhad completed upper secondary school, and who in year T were established in\nthe labour market or studying (including the Introduction Program IM). This\nnumber has been divided by the number of students in year T-1 who were\nregistered in the municipality, who had completed upper secondary school,\n(including IM).\n\n**Established in the labor market, it is**  \n_who is employed according to the definition of the employment register\n(November)  \n_ does not have any events that indicate unemployment or labor market policy\nmeasures that are not considered employment  \n* and have had an income that is not below a limit that is different for each year depending on the average percentage wage growth.\n\nIn 2016, the limit for being considered established in the labor market was\nSEK 191,800.\n\nStudents refer to both university studies and other education eligible for\nstudy grants, such as Komvux or folk high schools.\n\nSource: Statistics Sweden.\n\n"@en, "Antal elever i T-1, der var registreret i kommunen, som havde afsluttet\ngymnasiet, og som i T-1 var etableret på arbejdsmarkedet eller under\nuddannelse (inklusive introduktionsprogrammet IM). Dette tal er divideret med\nantallet af elever i T-1, der var registreret i kommunen, som havde afsluttet\ngymnasiet (inklusive IM).\n\n**Etableret på arbejdsmarkedet, er det**  \n_hvem er ansat i henhold til definitionen i beskæftigelsesregistret (november)  \n_ ikke har nogen hændelser, der indikerer arbejdsløshed eller\narbejdsmarkedspolitiske foranstaltninger, der ikke betragtes som beskæftigelse  \n* og har haft en indkomst, der ikke er under en grænse, der er forskellig for hvert år afhængigt af den gennemsnitlige procentvise lønvækst.\n\nI 2016 var grænsen for at blive betragtet som etableret på arbejdsmarkedet\n191.800 SEK.\n\nStuderende refererer til både universitetsstudier og anden uddannelse, der er\nberettiget til studiestøtte, såsom Komvux eller højskoler.\n\nKilde: Statistiska Centralbyrån.\n\n"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://www.geonames.org/2692965/malmoe.html>, _:b0__4050.
_:b0__4050 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#bbox> "POLYGON((12.8850967451 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.6421476735,13.1517619812 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.5022773196,12.8850967451 55.6421476735))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/4bc0a377-29f3-4bf6-94f2-a1ff243413a2> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/0e01ba1a25b24ce4d82683ada08cb166>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/4bc0a377-29f3-4bf6-94f2-a1ff243413a2/resource/7d61594a-386d-45ac-94cc-9ef203ffebaf>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-12-15"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T15:59:28.550011"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Ungdomar som är etablerade på arbetsmarknaden eller studerar 1 år efter fullföljd gymnasieutbildning"@sv, "Young people who are established in the labor market or studying 1 year after completing upper secondary education"@en, "Unge, der er etableret på arbejdsmarkedet eller studerer 1 år efter endt ungdomsuddannelse"@da;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#13975c2d6b2791be8ac35815d775525b>.
<#13975c2d6b2791be8ac35815d775525b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
