    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/d4acbc72-3834-4318-b1cd-761c61c7ef7b/resource/83aad6f4-d298-483d-8856-1db43ce54f5f>, <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/d4acbc72-3834-4318-b1cd-761c61c7ef7b/resource/06e78089-cdb7-48a6-b961-2cd668ca5227>;
