<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#a74727bfd72d3d17794fef33cacf3d73>.
<#a74727bfd72d3d17794fef33cacf3d73> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/228>;
