<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#54d42b89f8a538e67e39254ba69935d1>.
<#54d42b89f8a538e67e39254ba69935d1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/82a25769-80d5-4886-b441-c16dd025f249/resource/e299554e-b0a3-447f-9485-7fccbebba172>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-29T06:25:17.693Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#54d42b89f8a538e67e39254ba69935d1> {
<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/82a25769-80d5-4886-b441-c16dd025f249/resource/e299554e-b0a3-447f-9485-7fccbebba172> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-08-22T06:14:04.914462"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/availability> <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/availability/available>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#status> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/distribution-status/COMPLETED>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-25T12:34:44.241124"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://api.kolada.se/v2/data/municipality/1280/kpi/N15545>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Elever i åk 6 med lägst betyget E i matematik, hemkommun, andel (%) (N15545)"@sv, "Students in year 6 with a minimum grade of E in mathematics, home municipality, percentage (%) (N15545)"@en, "Elever i 6. klasse med minimum karakteren E i matematik, hjemkommune, procentdel (%) (N15545)"@da;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Samtliga uppgifter avser elever i skolor med betyg enligt det mål- och kunskapsrelaterade betygssystemet. Antal elever i årskurs 6 med lägst betyg E i matematik dividerat med antal elever som läst ämnet i årskurs 6. Multipliceras med 100 för redovisning i procent. Avser elever folkbokförda i kommunen oavsett var de går i skola. Elever med okänd bakgrund ingår. För dessa elever anges kommunen där de går i skolan som hemkommun. \nKälla: Kolada"@sv, "All data refers to students in schools with grades according to the goal- and\nknowledge-related grading system. Number of students in grade 6 with the\nlowest grade E in mathematics divided by the number of students who studied\nthe subject in grade 6. Multiplied by 100 for reporting as a percentage.\nRefers to students registered in the municipality regardless of where they\nattend school. Students with unknown backgrounds are included. For these\nstudents, the municipality where they attend school is stated as the home\nmunicipality. Source: Kolada\n\n"@en, "Alle data refererer til elever i skoler med karakterer i henhold til det mål-\nog vidensrelaterede karaktersystem. Antal elever i 6. klasse med den laveste\nkarakter E i matematik divideret med antallet af elever, der studerede faget i\n6. klasse. Ganget med 100 for rapportering som en procentdel. Refererer til\nelever registreret i kommunen uanset hvor de går i skole. Elever med ukendt\nbaggrund er inkluderet. For disse elever er den kommune, hvor de går i skole,\nangivet som hjemkommune. Kilde: Kolada\n\n"@da;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#7bc92186add2a8db10f277842f77d361>.
